{"tid":2058134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"危駕衝燈撞人 警罪成停牌候判","createTime":"2020-06-10T02:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T05:59:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d077e93f34fa69d5374d5c3b97bf6544d497f36a","tid":2058134,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/Z7CKQUOPBBIQD47IIR227Z54CE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FZ7CKQUOPBBIQD47IIR227Z54CE%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9dc1d686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FZ7CKQUOPBBIQD47IIR227Z54CE%2F&h=514b0e2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/Z7CKQUOPBBIQD47IIR227Z54CE/</a><br />\n<br />\n危駕衝燈撞人 警罪成停牌候判<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qYM01b_veIcMdb7NMjK0utAV1q8=/802x599/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QM2AIWJWOO3W4TBT2ENYAV274E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqYM01b_veIcMdb7NMjK0utAV1q8%3D%2F802x599%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQM2AIWJWOO3W4TBT2ENYAV274E.jpg&h=a82f94ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名警員聲稱深夜趕往救人，駕警車衝紅燈，將一名居住紀律部隊宿舍的夜歸婦撞至重傷，昨被裁定危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪名成立。裁判官指片段顯示被告切線時「畀油加速」，故他才會收掣不及。辯方指被告將面對內部紀律聆訊，其妻患癌，兩人育有一名歲半兒子，若遭革職，月入3.8萬元的他將難找其他工作，連帶失去住宿福利，望法庭判非監禁式刑罰，讓他有機會保留警隊工作。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳家傑（47歲，圓圖）在開審前承認不小心駕駛，但否認危駕罪受審，指他去年3月8日在秀茂坪康寧道與振華道交界撞倒女事主蔣一平（37歲）。裁判官莫子聰考慮到被告當時正執行職務，先索取社服令報告，押後至7月6日判刑，但先下令被告停牌30個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車cam片顯示加速致收掣不及<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n在可行情況下可無視交通燈，但衝紅燈非本案爭議點，當被告駕車駛至斑馬線時，必須加倍留心路面情況，因行人絕對有優先權過馬路。<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1545/19<br />\n■記者楊思雅"},{"pid":"e48de6c4bd7a20b717200d38bb9d1d035dc0482e","tid":2058134,"uid":224406,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"47歲死廢柴搵得果4皮野<br />\n狗乸生埋cancer<br />\n仲要養隻歲半狗仔<br />\n自己退休隻狗仔毛都未出一條<br />\n唔慣之得要賣冰啦<br />\n<br />\n呢d社會垃圾就攞去人道毀滅啦"},{"pid":"7f121cb88f50a0c04e7f52213b45249fd61332bf","tid":2058134,"uid":172485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"一時無成仲要咁老先搵隻雞幫佢生仔"},{"pid":"dbabd9bea89690c090aee5b00507c1969669cede","tid":2058134,"uid":172485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f121cb88f50a0c04e7f52213b45249fd61332bf","tid":2058134,"uid":172485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"一時無成仲要咁老先搵隻雞幫佢生仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"事"},{"pid":"da8ad6db7919a313e3ae9fa1059082717d2a3832","tid":2058134,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"上訴庭：警察可靠誠實，上訴得直控罪被撤銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413465b3a02d45dfee72f49449e356b24ab00a70","tid":2058134,"uid":38757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"可能內部洗腦太勁, 做野都係楂流灘架啦.....47 歳仲駁扎?...."},{"pid":"b7bced2e4d81d038be577cbe399690f2ee21f044","tid":2058134,"uid":89801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"佢撞到個人都係住宿舍<br />\n可能係警嫂 所以先會告得入<br />\n<br />\n如果傷者唔係住宿舍？咁咪告唔入囉"},{"pid":"6b212e2edfc4f55fddd52cbdedcbfbd7fb073ba1","tid":2058134,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7bced2e4d81d038be577cbe399690f2ee21f044","tid":2058134,"uid":89801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"佢撞到個人都係住宿舍<br />\n可能係警嫂 所以先會告得入<br />\n<br />\n如果傷者唔係住宿舍？咁咪告唔入囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"撞到大蛇架水砲車，今次佢仲唔仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c074feb3ad8e9f542dfcb1aa9d191d7b7d8b319","tid":2058134,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote